            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="ques-cont">
                <div class="small-cont">
                    <p class="question">
                        What types of courses does GenZ Academy offer?
    
                    </p>
                    <p class="answer">
                        We offer a wide range of courses, including coding, graphic design,
                        artificial intelligence, entrepreneurship, and more. Each course is
                        designed to be interactive and engaging for young learners.
    
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="small-cont">
                    <p class="question">
                        Are classes offered online, or do I need to attend in-person?
    
                    </p>
                    <p class="answer">
                        We offer both online and in-person classes to fit your needs. You can
                        learn from the comfort of home or join us on our
                        campus for a more hands-on experience.
    
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="small-cont">
                    <p class="question">
                        Who is eligible to join GenZ Academy?
    
                    </p>
                    <p class="answer">
                        GenZ Academy welcomes students aged 14-16 who are eager
                        to learn and build new skills, regardless of previous experience.
    
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="small-cont">
                    <p class="question">
                        Do I need any prior knowledge to join a course?
                    </p>
                    <p class="answer">
                        No prior experience is required! Our courses
                        are structured to support beginners and build
                        up knowledge step-by-step, so everyone can follow along.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="small-cont">
                    <p class="question">
                        How long do courses usually last?
    
                    </p>
                    <p class="answer">
                        Our courses range from 4 to 12 weeks, depending on
                        the topic and level. We balance length with focused
                        content to maximize learning and enjoyment.
    
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="small-cont">
                    <p class="question">
                        Will I receive a certificate after completing the course?
    
                    </p>
                    <p class="answer">
